# Authentication Testing

### Test auth endpoint
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/auth/test

### Register a new user
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "John",
  "lastName": "Doe",
  "username": "johndoe",
  "email": "john.doe@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "role": "USER"
}

### Register an admin user
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Admin",
  "lastName": "User",
  "username": "admin",
  "email": "admin@example.com",
  "password": "admin123",
  "role": "ADMIN"
}

### Login as regular user
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "johndoe",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Login as admin
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "admin123"
}

### Create contact (requires authentication)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/contacts/create-contact
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "firstName": "Jane",
  "lastName": "Smith",
  "otherName": "Marie",
  "email": "jane.smith@example.com",
  "phoneNumber": "1234567890",
  "address": "123 Main St, City, State"
}

### Get all contacts (user's own contacts)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/contacts/all-contacts
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### Get all contacts (admin only)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/contacts/admin/all-contacts
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### Get specific contact
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/contacts/contact-address/1
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### Update contact
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/v1/contacts/update-contact/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "firstName": "Jane Updated",
  "address": "456 New Address St"
}

### Delete contact (admin only)
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/v1/contacts/delete-contact/1
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### Search contacts
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/contacts/search-contact?firstName=Jane&email=jane
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE
